<i>for 48 million kilts</i>

246
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:49,840
<i>from the planet Skyron</i>
<i>in the galaxy of Andromeda.</i>

247
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:54,560
Angus, how are you going
