251
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:05,600
-Is that so?
-Aye.

252
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:07,320
And you've never been
further than Berwick-on-Tweed.

253
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:09,320
Aye.

254
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:11,120
