God willing.

267
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:53,560
He were a strange,
unearthly creature.

268
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:57,880
A quivering, glistening mass.

269
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:01,920
Angus Podgorny,
what do you mean?

270
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:06,840
