Alec and David--

274
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,760
Hang on.

275
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:19,800
-What?
-There's five.

276
00:17:19,840 --> 00:17:21,600
-What?
-Five people.

277
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:24,040
