go though, dear.

333
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:39,200
I didn't want
to seem ungrateful.

334
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:42,160
Oh, Angus, I will not let you
make a fool of yourself.

335
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:44,800
-But I must.
-Oh, no, you'll not.

336
00:19:44,840 --> 00:19:47,480
-Oh, Mary, Mary--
-[HINGES SQUEAK]

337
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:53,280
