348
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:30,800
So if you're going out,

349
00:20:30,840 --> 00:20:32,440
or going on holiday,

350
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:35,040
or anything strange happens
involving other galaxies,

351
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:37,320
