354
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:44,680
And the same goes for dogs.

355
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:48,640
So, I'm sorry to have
interrupted your exciting
science fiction story,

356
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:51,640
but then, crime's
our business, you know.

357
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:53,600
So carry on viewing,

358
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:55,320
and my thanks to the BBC

359
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:57,360
