this little chat with you.

360
00:20:57,400 --> 00:21:00,360
Good night. God bless.
Look after yourselves.

361
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,680
Do sit down, Mr. Podgorny.

362
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:05,600
I-- I think what's happened

363
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:08,000
