terribly funny--

364
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:09,920
Tragic.

365
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:12,920
You must understand that
we have to catch the creature
that ate your wife

366
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:15,680
and if you could just help us
answer a few questions

367
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:18,520
we may be able to help
save a few lives.

368
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:22,760
I know this is the way your wife
would have wanted it.

369
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:25,160
Aye, I'll do my best,
sergeant.

370
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,720
"Detective inspector."

371
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:30,320
Detective inspector.

372
00:21:30,360 --> 00:21:32,600
Now, then,
the facts are these:

