390
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:13,040
I'm afraid that's just
one of his stories.

391
00:22:13,080 --> 00:22:15,760
You must understand
that a blancmange
impersonator and cannibal

392
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:18,960
has to use some pretty clever
stories to allay suspicion.

393
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,120
-Then you mean--
-Yes.

394
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,840
-But-- Yes.
-How? Well--

395
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,440
-Not! Why?
-I'm afraid so.

396
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:24,440
-Who knows. Could be. I know.
