404
00:22:42,080 --> 00:22:43,800
[SCREAMS]

405
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:58,600
So everyone in England
is being turned
into Scotsmen, right?

406
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:00,960
Yes.

407
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:02,240
Now, which is the worst

408
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:04,360
tennis-playing nation
