409
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:06,280
Um, Australia.

410
00:23:06,320 --> 00:23:08,200
-No. Try again.
-Australia?

411
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:10,480
No, try again but say
a different place.

412
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:12,920
Oh, I thought you meant
I said it badly.

