415
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:20,160
-Of course.
-Now...

416
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:22,640
Now, these blancmanges,

417
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:25,880
apart from the one
that killed Mrs. Podgorny,

